<HEAD>Groom's Brother Leaves Gifts In Back Of Cab</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Somewhere out there is a cab with a trunkful of
wedding presents that belong to a pair of newlyweds.
   Tom and Betsy McCormack were married Sunday night and celebrated
with about 100 friends and relatives.
   After the reception, they invited their closest relatives back
to their suite at the Barbizon Hotel across town to open the gifts.
